{"tid":1703787,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[真。文具] 一人一支筆","createTime":"2019-11-10T12:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:35:18.000Z","uid":179179,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"25b035d26a970ef8920ce5a67671505b70e64495","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"我都係見手足見到先上網睇下，所以都係新手，旨在講下建議，啱聽就幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次想講下<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">戰術筆</span></span></strong><br />\n戰術筆起源於美國，最初主要是在武器和裝備愛好者中流傳，現在，戰術筆已成為<span style=\"color: red;\">普通消費者外出旅行與汽車車主的必帶裝備。</span><br />\n另外，戰術筆具有<span style=\"color: red;\">優秀的書寫功能及細膩的外觀，適合商務、白領人士作為日常高級簽字筆使用。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要寫靚字</span><br />\n<br />\n咁戰術筆又係咩嚟呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8tzov5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8tzov5.jpg&h=8734b902&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一般有12-16cm長<br />\n戰術筆屬於防禦型工具，且具有良好的隱蔽性，可隨身攜帶，便於日常防衛<br />\n筆尖的其中一端為鋼錐，可輕易粉碎玻璃<br />\n表面紋理和防滑處理上非常下功夫，有很好的防脫手處理<br />\n在使用的時候，手指需要承載較大的衝擊力，只有筆身微微下凹的戰術筆，才很舒服<br />\n<br />\n市面上常見的戰術筆大部分採用航空鋁或者鈦合金製作，堅固耐用，不易損壞，而市面上的原子筆一般採用塑料，即便鋼筆是金屬也是比較脆的金屬，在進行自我防衛動作，敲擊等動作時，可能會折斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tc.sinaimg.cn/maxwidth.800/tc.service.weibo.com/mmbiz_qpic_cn/5ebfa3f148031aaf90ac7f26a0f715a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftc.sinaimg.cn%2Fmaxwidth.800%2Ftc.service.weibo.com%2Fmmbiz_qpic_cn%2F5ebfa3f148031aaf90ac7f26a0f715a1.jpg&h=45dfd233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但用戰術筆係依賴身體力量同技巧，例如打邊度同要求配合雙手同手臂，而引導對方的被攻擊點到一個適合攻擊的位置"},{"pid":"562fda161742989456a01121283b8b35ba1aa532","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"998c92da3ef342e572101296561e85b3789672f7","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"9ebdd79af880774bd9787d35eaeb018018847226","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"1d41d9b512a09d14f98244e979197cb27755f341","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"0c2a0a6f357c2e455bebc5db35ab30fc74a7527f","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"ad79d680718dd6657814d9bea79e4710ab73bb1e","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"1070ceadb6135257c067de1795c70bdcee2d192b","tid":1703787,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"老實講,越短既武器越需要訓練先用到<br />\n唔同刀仔棍呢D學幾下就用到"},{"pid":"ed79a543699d63ac14b2282f7ec8808816d4227f","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"推7/10"},{"pid":"8f5b2c888637a9f38c832699cc51514be6cead8b","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1070ceadb6135257c067de1795c70bdcee2d192b","tid":1703787,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"老實講,越短既武器越需要訓練先用到<br />\n唔同刀仔棍呢D學幾下就用到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"係 我都有提過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但混亂期間用到 同埋易收藏"},{"pid":"fb171498de63a3270bb670520c42551f99c91946","tid":1703787,"uid":179179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"推8/10"},{"pid":"5d